arXiv preprint arXiv:2512.08782, 2025;Hackers may create malicious solidity programs and deploy it in the Ethereum block chain. These malicious smart contracts try to attack legitimate programs by exploiting its vulnerabilities such as reentrancy, tx. origin attack, bad randomness, deligatecall and so on.
